snippet: In a show of strength, lawmakers in Parliament derailed the candidacy of Alenka Bratusek, a former prime minister of Slovenia.
lead_paragraph: In a show of strength, lawmakers in Parliament derailed the candidacy of Alenka Bratusek, a former prime minister of Slovenia.
